overview: Put your dancing shoes on and enjoy the Show! Prima Princessa features the world-renowned Paris Operat Ballet performing excerpts from Swan Lake, narrated by the adorable Prima Princessa herself! Between acts, Prima Princessa guides you through ballet steps demonstrated by the School of American Ballet students. You can become a Prima Princess ballerina, too!
tagline: Put your dancing shoes on and enjoy the show!
title: Prima Princess Presents Swan Lake
